===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# To measure the duration (amount of time) an action takes.
# To [[measure]] the [[speed]] of an object.
#: ''He was '''clocked''' at 155 miles per hour.''
# To [[hit]] someone: ''When the boxer let down his guard, his opponent clocked him.''
#{{slang}} To take notice of : '''''Clock''' the wheels on that car!''   
#{{slang}} To falsify the [[odometer]] reading of a vehicle (slang).   
#: ''That's never done only 40,000. It's been '''clocked.''''' 

